    %section
      .company-example
        .company-example__description
          %h3 Hummings
          %p.date.company-example__service-used BUILD: STRATEGY, DESIGN, ENGINEERING
          %p
            Hummings is a mobile-first personal finance companion app. They came to me with early stage wireframes, and I guided them through UX revisions and product development. Once designs were finalized, I put together a small engineering team to build out the entire app.
            / %a.read-more{href:"#"} Read More &rsaquo;
          %p
            %a.read-more{href:"https://www.hellohummings.com/", target: "_blank"} VISIT SITE
            
        .company-example__image.omega
          %a{href:"https://www.hellohummings.com/", target: "_blank"}
            = image_tag "work/hummings.png", alt: "Hummings"
        .company-example__testimony
          %blockquote
            %p We started working with Pavan at Gray Bike for our MVP app (www.hellohummings.com) at the wireframe stage. Pavan quickly grasped the vision of our product and provided a great deal of insights to shape our UX, product architecture, and the engineering milestones. He also came up with really smart solutions to leverage existing tools & frameworks to optimize the custom coding work.
            %p Throughout the project, Pavan was professional, prompt, reliable, and communicated very well. He is very methodical, tested rigorously, and was very smart about figuring out the bugs. He also worked hard to make sure the project delivered on time - we were actually a week early. This was the most enjoyable and "glitch-free" software development experience I've had to-date.
            %p Our ultimate product was clean, beautiful, and stable. Pavan was more than an engineer. He was an integral part of our product team. We really enjoyed working with him and would happily recommend him to anyone looking for a technical partner for their next project.
            %cite Katherine Chen, Founder at Hummings

